  Type: 0
  QuestionTextAR: "\u0625\u064A\u0645\u062A\u0649 \u0631\u062D \u062A\u062A\u062C\u0648\u0632
    \u064A\u0627 \u0627\u0628\u0646\u064A\u061F"
  Choices:
  - TextAR: "\u0645\u0627 \u0623\u062F\u0631\u064A \u0628\u0639\u062F\u064A\u0646"
    BatteryDelta: -0.2
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 0
    ScrapReward: 2
    IsCorrect: 0
    FeedbackText: Vague deflection signals discomfort and creates awkward silence.
      Redirect warmly instead.
  - TextAR: "\u0625\u0646 \u0634\u0627\u0621 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u064A\u0627
      \u062E\u0627\u0644\u062A\u064A \u0639\u0642\u0628\u0627\u0644 \u0639\u0631\u0633\u0643"
    BatteryDelta: 0.15
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 10
    ScrapReward: 5
    IsCorrect: 1
    FeedbackText: "This phrase redirects the blessing back to her family \u2014 the
      socially elegant Jordanian answer."
  - TextAR: "\u0647\u0627\u062F \u0645\u0627 \u0625\u0644\u0643 \u0634\u063A\u0644
      \u0641\u064A\u0647"
    BatteryDelta: -0.4
    StomachDelta: 0
    EidiaReward: 0
    ScrapReward: 0
    IsCorrect: 0
    FeedbackText: "This response is considered extremely \u0631\u0641\u0636 \u0648\u0642\u062D.
      The robot has caused a family incident."
